{"tid":1379492,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"（突發）全民拒換證行動！！","createTime":"2019-07-28T19:51:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T20:52:54.000Z","uid":229437,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"95f6462e7bca9b2efa32c093e7a3ccbff0e3ce33","tid":1379492,"uid":229437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T19:51:30.000Z","msg":"/轉發/<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/738178659931814/posts/748276378922042?s=731303153&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F738178659931814%2Fposts%2F748276378922042%3Fs%3D731303153%26sfns%3Dmo&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4Zyy0trSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=71dbec9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/738178659931814/posts/748276378922042?s=731303153&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iqSM6c1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiqSM6c1.png&h=7297a947&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為一個 雲海 陳雲海 fans, 陰謀論當然不離口。政府個 「監控燈柱」係計劃於2021至2022年度完成，咁啱「新智能身份證」又係plan左2022年完成，兩個計劃都具有無線射頻識別(RFID)系統。你同我講話兩個企劃的資料唔互通我就信呀? 壽終正寢我都唔信呀~! 你老味轉個頭又加左n個CCTV係狗鐡同政總，信你老味! <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">順從政府換新證，之後走去買個套入住根本on9 。你俾人強姦，唔通話「插唔係唔得，戴個套我放心俾你姦啦。」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n直頭要唔換!!!! 連同個濕鳩「多功能智慧燈柱試驗計劃」一齊做低佢! <br />\n<br />\n雲海話過，佢幾年前試過就身份證問題質政府，當時政府話使用(現任)智能身份證以後永遠都唔會換證。但suddenly 2015 年保安局要求換新證。Well, 2014 發生乜事令到2015保安局要嗱嗱聲搞新身分證，大家都估到la。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我唔換證<br />\n我唔要監控燈柱<br />\n我唔信政府</span></span><br />\n<br />\n(1985或1986年出生的人已經換左，而家換班老人。等你冇乜危機意識，2021年就換90後丶全部80後)<br />\n#壽終正寢 #我唔換證 #智能身份證 #多功能智慧燈柱 #RFID #無線射頻識別 #監控燈柱 #我唔要監控燈柱"},{"pid":"d5169c9cdd85d0a334428992cd4f1e36dffdc080","tid":1379492,"uid":256671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T19:53:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6eef4862f40b9180f1f804baf3488c64e3a8793f","tid":1379492,"uid":207476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T19:56:55.000Z","msg":"8月5號齊罷工"},{"pid":"5208eb5e9c2fcee663bb85d5fbd22e6c1902d63a","tid":1379492,"uid":229437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T20:01:50.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da26a4873b68e6a8ee8fc2f5076f714f64756d4a","tid":1379492,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T20:08:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfdce0d275261d9412ce5f156cded42551254bb7","tid":1379492,"uid":229437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T20:09:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">8月5號齊罷工</span></span>"},{"pid":"9c40e631f9fc5e9ed99b8f020f243b532eca2670","tid":1379492,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T20:11:04.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"e73f5e13ffb63255dd8d6c92c57649c1202f7788","tid":1379492,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T20:52:54.000Z","msg":"Twitch疑向中共跪低！直播香港示威帳號永久封鎖 輸入1989等字眼被禁言<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379562\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379562</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}